desc: Dupree's Vintage is a combination antique and record store located in South Milwaukee, WI. We specialize in mid-century clothing, decor, and accessories along with a selection of new and used vinyl ranging from funk and jazz to rock and country. We even have some rap and electronic music for good measure.

layout.text: Dupree's is a vintage shop specializing in Mid Century clothing, décor, furnishings & records - retro through current.
